# Auto Pipeline — Audit Report

## Methodology
Full cross-audit of [core/auto_pipeline.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/auto_pipeline.py) and [ui/auto_pipeline_tab.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/auto_pipeline_tab.py) against the 3 existing tabs:
- **YouTube tab** ([ui/youtube_tab.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/youtube_tab.py)) — Download flow
- **Chapter tab** ([ui/chapter_tab.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/chapter_tab.py)) — Split flow  
- **Style Rewrite tab** ([ui/rewrite_style_tab.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py)) — Rewrite delegation

